1954;;She Couldn't Say No;;American;;Lloyd Bacon;;Robert Mitchum, Jean Simmons;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/She_Couldn%27t_Say_No_(1954_film);;Wealthy Corby Lane (Jean Simmons) visits the American hamlet of Progress, Arkansas, whose residents had paid for a critical medical operation for her when she was a child. She decides to express her gratitude by giving them money anonymously. The headstrong woman clashes with the local doctor, Robert Sellers (Robert Mitchum), who foresees the resulting chaos.